            <thetext>As posted on the mailing list (see [1]):

The virtual list currently does not provide a method to force a refresh explicitly. At the moment a refresh can only be forced by clearing and resetting the delegate property. A method such as list.refresh() would be a better way to do this.

I think this might also apply to the VirtualTree, VirtualComboBox and VirtualSelectBox.

[1] http://sourceforge.net/mailarchive/message.php?msg_id=27318209</thetext>
